overview: For the first issue we got one of Switzerland's finest newcomers "Claudio 'c2' Bohli", a sweet montage section featuring Dave Benski, Men Cheung, Daniel Prell, David Tadjibaev and some other cool dudes, a back in the days section featuring German legends Schillings, Peterka and Parobeck, and a mind blowing profile with another German legend: Guido Rosenkranz!
title: Hey Dude: Issue 1
